[SPEAKER_00] normalno počne koškanje, udaranje.

907
00:44:48,000 --> 00:44:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na tezanje.

908
00:44:49,000 --> 00:44:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma nije na tezanje.

909
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I mi svi dole.

910
00:44:52,000 --> 00:44:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tuča.

911
00:44:53,000 --> 00:44:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bez tim tuča.

912
00:44:54,000 --> 00:44:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači sad ti braniš igrača, ovo ono.

913
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I hajde, to se balo.

914
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je svega.

915
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, bilo stvarno svega.

916
00:45:02,000 --> 00:45:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] uletla policija.

917
00:45:04,000 --> 00:45:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bila je tu pratnja.

918
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je tu možda nekih sedam, osam navijača.

919
00:45:08,000 --> 00:45:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, navijača, ljudi koji su bili izdevortirani,

920
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] neriješili naši rezultate.

921
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] I možda njegovom nekom reakcijom.

922
00:45:15,000 --> 00:45:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ne znamo mi tačno.

923
00:45:16,000 --> 00:45:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerovatno je ono nešto rukama malo.

924
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad smo se mi tu...

925
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je bilo malo udaranja i guranja.

926
00:45:24,000 --> 00:45:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si ti trenirao hrvanje štisino?

927
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerovatno to među prvima.

928
00:45:28,000 --> 00:45:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne, sad ja sjedem nazad, u autobusu idemo.

929
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu už smo mi.

930
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo je svaka uteknica finale.

931
00:45:37,000 --> 00:45:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti sad izgubio si dva boda.

932
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Galata Sarajl, mislim da je tad Galata birao,

933
00:45:43,000 --> 00:45:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] pobjegla ti je dva.

934
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ti već u to sljedeća uteknica čekaš pod stresom.

935
00:45:50,000 --> 00:45:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sjedem kontran Čevića,

936
00:45:52,000 --> 00:45:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] tri dana stojena ljudi nas da čekalo.

937
00:45:56,000 --> 00:45:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ne suku ovdje.

938
00:45:58,000 --> 00:46:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sada malo na reprezentaciju.

939
00:46:04,000 --> 00:46:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Puno kvalitetnih i dobrih imena suigrača je bilo u reprezentaciji,

940
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali je bilo malo rezultata.

941
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Daj nam malo taj put od tvojeg početka do kraja.

942
00:46:16,000 --> 00:46:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kada sad sve, kad prođu godine i kad pogledaš sve to,

943
00:46:20,000 --> 00:46:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da, da li je realno ili nerealno, ne znam.

944
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:30,000
