956
00:47:02,000 --> 00:47:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] je bilo nerealno očekivati sa tada.

957
00:47:06,000 --> 00:47:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, drugačiji je sistem igranja bio.

958
00:47:08,000 --> 00:47:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorim ti, tada je išao jedan iz grupe.

959
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si počeo iz, ne znam, pete,

960
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] jako smo bili u Nova Zemlja.

961
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] kreću si od nule.

962
00:47:16,000 --> 00:47:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda smo se mi tu borili sa opremom.

963
00:47:20,000 --> 00:47:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, smijeti što je bio kada.

964
00:47:24,000 --> 00:47:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je to bilo, ono, improvizacija,

965
00:47:26,000 --> 00:47:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali smo mi to shvatali.

966
00:47:28,000 --> 00:47:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda vidiš da se tu već i dešavale neke stvari

